{"word":"G4624 - σκανδαλίζω - skandalízō - skan-dal-id'-zo - Offend","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σκανδαλίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>skandalízō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>skan-dal-id'-zo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Offend"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - இடறலடை, இடறலுண்டாக்கு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to put a stumbling - block"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> To &ldquo;scandalize&rdquo;; from <a href=\"#/G4625 - σκάνδαλον - skándalon - skan'-dal-on/4625\">G4625</a>; to <i>entrap</i>, that is, <i>trip</i> up (figuratively <i>stumble</i> [transitively] or <i>entice</i> to sin, apostasy or displeasure): - (make to) offend."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G4624 - σκανδαλίζω - skandalízō - skan-dal-id'-zo/4624\">G4624</a>, <a href=\"#/G4625 - σκάνδαλον - skándalon - skan'-dal-on/4625\">G4625</a>"}]}